front.title: •Wakeelmui (V)
front.gametext: Dark:  Your TIEs may deploy here as a 'react.'  Light:  While opponent has more starships here than you, your starships here are power -1.

pulledBy: You Cannot Hide Forever & Mobilization Points
combo: Wakeelmui + Sienar Fleet Systems Retrieve 1 Force each time you deploy a TIE. Once per turn may relocate a TIE just lost from table to Used Pile.
